Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of\Nour new fall offerings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might want to maximize\Nthe sweetness of the chestnuts more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But really, what's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's only just started, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't get a jump on it now,\Nwe won't be done in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I just can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that you can't cook when\Nyou have the best taste buds of us all, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I knew that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm off to let Dad\Nknow what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm the one who\N asked you to be our taster,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but don't you think you've been\Nputting on some pounds lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better watch out, or you're\Ngonna get chubby in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine! I am watching my weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Easy enough for me to say, but\NI do eat a lot of sweets these days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's been a while since\NI last got on that scale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not getting much exercise, either,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I'd better take\Nbetter care of my body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way... No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did this happen after only\Na few days of not weighing myself?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I admit I have a pretty good\Nidea what the cause is,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but how could I have gained\Nthis much so suddenly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Outwardly, I don't look\Nthat much different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But am I the only one who thinks that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other people's eyes, does\Nthis tummy look enormous?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, Haru did point that out just now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! I've got to\Nfix this right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:54.26,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I Want to Lose Weight"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ruri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I've\Ngained weight lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't look any\Ndifferent than usual to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. You might want to\Nbe a little careful about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it, I've put on weight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know they say it's hard to notice\Nthe changes in your own body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I really had no clue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I started off by skipping breakfast,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but to slim down, first, I need to\Nexercise, right? And also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Morning, Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last thing I want is for Ichijo\Nto find out I've gained weight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to shed these\Npounds before he does!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, I'm gonna do this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starting today, no sweets whatsoever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm going to go easy on\Nmeals, as much as I can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.32,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GURRRRR!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, now, what was\Nthat sound, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake? You think\Nit was an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really, now! Why did my\Nstomach have to growl now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure, I skipped breakfast today,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but there's no need to growl that loudly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right, Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You kinda look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? No, no... It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.73,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GURRRRR!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-You've got to hang in there, Kosaki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You only have to suffer\Nfor now... It's only for now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once you've lost those extra pounds,\Nyou can eat like you always did!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you remember about\Nour date today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Classes can't end soon enough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Date? What was that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, what we've\Nall been talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to that\Nall-you-can-eat cake place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did we really say\Nwe were going to do that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.39,DefaultBot,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, we talked about it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I remember!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's that yummy-looking cake shop\Nthat was on TV the other day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I've already made up\Nmy mind about this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I have an emergency today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, really? Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just as well,\Nyou know, Young Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You went to have all-you-can-eat cake\Nyesterday and the day before as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating too much cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just wanted to\Ncompare the shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the same with Ruri, too.\NWhere does all the food go, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't understand it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All this talk of cake is\Nmaking me hungrier than ever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's only second period now, so\Nthere's still a way to go before lunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want my stomach to start\Ngrowling in the classroom again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a place like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to die, I wish I could just die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A girl getting caught\Neating lunch early...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How am I supposed to talk to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought, Onodera's\Nacting a little weird today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wonder if she's under the weather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or maybe something's bugging her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Everyone's going somewhere...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was our next class again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gym! That's right, I've got to\Nexercise, exercise!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have time to sit around moping!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to do whatever I can\Nto lose weight today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I've got to exercise!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna exercise and forget\Nhow I messed up just now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the girls are swimming today, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm hopeless in the water.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And besides, I'd rather not get into\Nan outfit that will expose my body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no! No whining, now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say that swimming's a good way\Nto lose weight! I've got to give it my all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, today you're pumped up, for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Want to\Npractice with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can go at your pace, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never thought I'd end up drowning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I was totally weak\Nfrom not having eaten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I toughed it out for one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wonder if anything changed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I think for a second that\NI've lost weight in a single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I've gained weight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so much, too! No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I've hardly eaten a thing today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Onodera, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on with her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she feeling sick, after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I heard she collapsed\Nduring gym yesterday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, I wish I could\Nhelp her somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on! Muster up\Nsome courage, Raku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That konnyaku I boiled in soy sauce\Nthe other day... you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, this time I asked Miyamoto\Nwhat your favorites were beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I made these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candied sweet potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-Why did you have to do that now?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My favorite food is right before my eyes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do? I want to eat them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They smell so amazing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Ichijo for you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One look and you can\Ntell they're delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me he made them just for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, I can't! I can't! I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've already decided\Nnot to eat anything today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I gained even more\Nweight yesterday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... Ichijo did go to the trouble\Nof making them for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One bite can't hurt...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One bite can't hurt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to\Nforce yourself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, see, I'm not hungry right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry I'm not hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so serious she can't even\Ngulp down her favorite food?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she really okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to eat them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were delicious for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Ichijo made them just for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm such an idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing, anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just spinning my wheels again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of my selfishness,\NI ended up hurting Ichijo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How should I apologize to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if he'll let me try them again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-How about some tea, Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I stuck my nose\Nwhere it didn't belong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it seemed like you hadn't\Nbeen eating much lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought it would be easier\Nif it were something you liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is anything bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind talking\Nto me, I'll be happy to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he was worried about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel so bad about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When it's all my fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... what am I gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That makes me happy, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure? If that's the case, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you better make sure\Nyou at least eat right, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're thin, Onodera,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you gotta eat right\Nor you'll pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that\Nsmirk on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's been bugging you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, the problem's been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you know that scale's busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me sooner!\NI nearly had a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.65,Title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Good Morning"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Kosaki Onodera.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was a third year in junior high,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fell in love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fell in love with my\Nclassmate, Raku Ichijo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't as if he was exceptionally\Ngood at schoolwork or sports,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it was that simple, inner\Ngentleness that I was so in love with.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When we were second years,\Nwe became classmates for the first time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and as third years, we finally got to\Nbe speaking acquaintances.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But normally, we had no real contact.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I hardly ever went out of\Nmy way to talk to him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but saying "good morning" in the morning,\Nand "see you" after class...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was what\NI looked forward to everyday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:49.46,DefaultMid2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otori Girls' High School{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Raku,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you've already narrowed it down\Nto just one high school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Bonyari High.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying for Bonyari too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you can't beat\Nthe short commute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's hang out\Ntogether again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be stuck with you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem? You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Needless to say...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once we go on to high school, I won't\Nbe able to see Ichijo anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pretty soon, I won't be able to say\N"good morning" or "see you..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That would be so sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be with Ichijo longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to talk to him more,\Nabout so many things!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri! I'm going to take the exam\Nfor Bonyari High School!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you were\Ngoing for Otori Girls' High?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's tons of yummy\Ncake shops around there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... that's... Yes, I did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, Ichijo says\Nhe's going to Bonyari High, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll go to Bonyari, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Ruri, I thought you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know which college I want to go to,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but as far as high school goes,\Nit doesn't really matter which I attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even though Bonyari's not\Na selective school by any means,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's still gonna be hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since your grades are pretty low.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I started studying\Nfor the entrance exam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.85,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}National High School Entrance Exam\NQuestionnaire Compilation - English{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go to the same school\Nas the boy I loved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An ulterior motive, yes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but for someone who'd never in her fifteen\Nyears had a clear dream or goal in mind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there was no greater goal than that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I think I studied harder\Nthan I ever had before in my life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.63,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bonyari High School Entrance Exam Site
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The day of the exam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you taking\Nthe exam for Bonyari, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, actually, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you would've told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right... is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it our best\Nshot today, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both get in, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, I had\Nthe burning conviction that I'd pass.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought you'd be\Nway more freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, I studied so hard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Ruri helped me out so much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now all I have to do is\Ngive it my best shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to pass for sure, just like him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, all that\Nwork was for nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can never say\N"good morning" to him again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he'll never say\N"see you" to me again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go, Kosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Kosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come back here! Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, this looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister's turned into graffiti!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can never look Ruri or\NIchijo in the eye again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is so sad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'd known this was going to happen,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I'd just told him how I felt...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about you, Ichijo?\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting ready for\Ntomorrow's orientation, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My heart's flipping and flopping,\Neven at a time like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be the biggest idiot on Earth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Ichijo didn't go into it any further.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really is kind-hearted, Ichijo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only I could go to the same\Nschool as him, I'd be so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, aren't you\Ncold, dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to use my scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? N-N-No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:19:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just seeing you like that is\Nmaking me feel chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. You're going to\Ncatch a cold, Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, so just use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right... really!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, I'll use it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be okay with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now we kind of seem like\Nboyfriend and girlfriend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty long, huh? This scarf...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone at the house has\Nbeen knitting up a storm lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've got like a huge surplus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is hand-knitted?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel so happy, but could this be\Nmy chance to confess my feelings?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I could never...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onodera...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sorry! It's my mom calling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, answer it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I passed?
